GNOME Utilities - 
=================
Version: 2.10.x

GNOME Utilities for the GNOME 2.10 Desktop contains the following -

	gnome-system-log	[logview]
	gnome-search-tool	[gseachtool]
	gnome-dictionary	[gdictsrc]
	gfloppy			[gfloppy]
	gnome-screenshot	[gscreenshot]

Requirements -

	intltool	>= 0.29
	gnome-common	>= 2.3.0
	gtk+            >= 2.6.0
	libgnome	>= 2.5.0
	libgnomeui	>= 2.5.0
	gnome-desktop   >= 2.9.91
	libglade	>= 2.3.0
	libbonoboui	>= 2.1.0
	libgnomevfs	>= 2.8.4
	libpanel-applet >= 2.9.4
	libgnomeprintui >= 2.8.0

	
The following configure flags can be used -

	--enable-console-helper=no/yes  Enable PAM console helper [default=no]

	--enable-hal=yes/no  Enable HAL support for gfloppy [default=yes]

Installation -

See the file 'INSTALL'

How to report bugs -

See the file 'BUGS'
